messages.content: Hello! I'm happy to chat. What brings you here?
Doing well! What's on your mind today?
Cat is an animal and mammal. It has fur, tail and whiskers. It can meow, purr and climb.
Dog is an animal and mammal. It has fur, tail and paws. It can bark, run and fetch.
That's outside my current knowledge. What can you tell me about it?
Nice to meet you, Alice! What would you like to talk about?
I'm not certain about that. Could you share what you know so I can learn?
I want to give you a good answer, but I'm not sure. Can you help me understand better?
